thread.title: Sara Thelen
thread.title_full: Sheenco Travel reviewed by Sara Thelen

author: Sara Thelen
title: Sara Thelen
text: Our vacation was seamless. From the first time I talked to them on the phone, to the itinerary, to pick up and drop offs at the airports. The luxury cars we rode in were so lovely. Our driver Jerry was awesome and knowledgeable and took us off the beaten path as we requested. I have & will recommend Sheenco Travel for that dream trip to Ireland. I plan on coing back!!
